# Requirements

## MDPO

https://github.com/mondeja/mdpo

```
pip istall mdpo
```

## Pandoc (optional)

```
sudo apt-get install pandoc
```

## Texlive (optional)

On Ubuntu:

```
sudo apt-get install texlive-latex-recommended texlive-latex-extra texlive-xetex
```

## Poedit

```
sudo apt-get install poedit
```

# How to Generate the po file

```
./init.sh
```

# How to Generate the translated document 

```
./gera.sh
```

